| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4982 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1647ca71-c586-550a-8541-e8bcdaf76f02"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
